STATE of North Carolina
v.
Sulyaman Alisla WASALAAM No. 435P15-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 21, 2018 Sulyaman Alislam Wasalaam, for Wasalaam, Sulyaman Alisla. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 21st of November 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Scotland County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 21st of November 2018."
